zialer Arbeit wäre damit ein brauchbares, innovatives Konzept an die Hand gegeben.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aAIDSxSozialarbeitxProfessionalität. 4aAIDS-Hilfen. 4aGender Studies. 4aGesellschaft. 4aKörper. 4aProfessionelle Identität. 4aPädagogik. 4aQueer Theory. 4aSozialarbeit. 4aSozialpädagogik. 7aEDUCATION / General.2bisacsh  aBody.  aGender Studies.  aPedagogy.  aSocial Pedagogy.  aSocial Work.  aSociety.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102523008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Complete Package 2000-2009z9783110463415oZDB-23-TSO08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Highlight Collection Sozialw. 2000-2009z9783110463392oZDB-23-TSW0 cprintz978389942717240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839407172?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839407172423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839407172/original  a978-3-11-102523-0  transcript Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-TSOc2000d2009  aZDB-23-TSWc2000d2009